"    Congenital syphilis: Rash on soles",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 432px; height: 233px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Pigmented lesions on the soles of an infant with congenital syphilis.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
